title: Spark - Streaming
date:  2025-04-01
author: Wall Liu

Tng quan

c thm l thuyt v d liu streaming ti y hoc y
Spark Streaming l mt b m rng ca core Spark API cho php m rng, thng lng cao, c kh nng chu li. Spark Streaming c thit k x l d liu dng streams.

D liu u vo t Spark c th ly t Kafka, Flume, Kinesis (mt tool ca aws) hocTCP sockets l cc d liu ng c gi vo lin tc v c th c x l s dng cc thut ton phc tp vi cc hm high-level nh map, reduce, join v window. Cui cng, d liu sau khi x l c th lu tr ti cc h thng file system nh HDFS, databases, hoc hin th trc tip trn dashboards.

Spark Streaming nhn d liu u vo v chia chng thnh cc batches, sau chng c x l bi Spark engine to ra lung kt qu cui cng theo l.

Vi core Spark chng ta c bit v lm quen vi RDD, tuy nhin vi Spark Streaming chng ta khng th lm vic vi RDD c m thay vo Spark Streaming cung cp mt high-level abstraction c gi l DStream (discretized stream).

DStream Operation

C 3 loi Operation l:

  • Input operation
  • Transformation operation
  • Output operation

Input Operation

Mi Input Operation u c lin kt trc tip vi 1 i tng no , c 2 loi streaming source l:

  • Basic source: Socket, file,
  • Advanced source: Kafka, Twitter,
    V d Basic source - socket connection:
`   JavaReceiverInputDStream<String> lines = jsc.socketTextStream("localhost", 9999);   `

V d Advanced source - Kafka :

JavaInputDStream<ConsumerRecord<String, String>> stream;

stream = KafkaUtils.createDirectStream(jssc,LocationStrategies.PreferConsistent()

,ConsumerStrategies.Subscribe(topics, SSKafkaProperties.getInstance()));

Transformations

Cng ging vi Spark RDD, transformations gip bin i d liu u vo a ra d liu ph hp vi yu cu u ra. DStream h tr nhiu transformations c sn hn so vi Spark RDD.

map(func)

Tr v mt tp d liu mi bng cch chuyn i mi phn t c sang tng phn t mi thng qua func.

V d chng trnh sau vit hoa ton b chui k t u vo:

JavaReceiverInputDStream<String> input = jsc.socketTextStream("localhost", 9999);
JavaDStream<String> upcase = input.map(new Function<String, String>() {
	private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;

	@Override
	public String call(String value) throws Exception {
		return value.toUpperCase();
	} 
});

upcase.print();

S bin i ca map l 1-1 khi mt u vo xin chao toi la s cho ra mt u ra XIN CHAO TOI LA.

flatMap(func)

Ging mi map, tuy nhin map l chuyn i 1-1 cn vi flatMap th c th l chuyn i 1-N, 1-1, 1-0.

V d trong chng trnh di y s tch mt chui k t u vo thnh danh sch cc t:

JavaReceiverInputDStream<String> input = jsc.socketTextStream("localhost", 9999);
JavaDStream<String> words = input.flatMap(new FlatMapFunction<String, String>() {
	private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;

	@Override
	public Iterator<String> call(String value) throws Exception {
		List<String> listString = Arrays.asList(value.split(" "));
		return listString.iterator();
	}
});

words.print();

S bin i y khng cn l 1-1 na, khi chui k t u vo l xin chao toi la trannguyenhan th ta s c mt danh sch gm 5 u ra ln lt l xin, chao, toi, la, trannguyenhan.

filter(func)

Tr v mt DStream mi bng vic ly ra mt s gi tr c chn lc qua hm func.

V d trong chng trnh di y lc v tr ra nhng dng u vo c cha t error:

JavaReceiverInputDStream<String> input = jsc.socketTextStream("localhost", 9999);
JavaDStream<String> lines = input.filter(new Function<String, Boolean>() {
	private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;

	@Override
	public Boolean call(String value) throws Exception {
		return value.contains("error");
	}
});

lines.print();

Output Operation

Output Operation cho php d liu ca DStream c y ra cc h thng bn ngoi nh c s d liu hoc h thng tp. Mt s cc output operation v d nh l print() m chng ta s dng 3 v d trong Transformations Operation bn trn in d liu ra ngoi terminal.

Ngoi ra, chng ta cn mt s cc Output Operation khc nh:

  • saveAsTextFiles
  • saveAsObjectFiles
  • saveAsHadoopFiles
  • foreachRDD
